The interpolation is always done strictly following numeric rules. If
you want to interpolate upwards from 127 to 0, then you have to substitute
0 by the texture width.  You should see, that the 3d hardware can't guess how
you would like to do the interpolation, you have to define it exactly, so that
no misunderstandements can occur.

